As of January 2018 , the total number of people in food intake is estimated to be just as high as 1 % of the total food intake , as indicated by the total number of people affected by food shortage , as well as the total amount of food shortage , as per 1 % of the total population affected by food shortage , as indicated by the total number of people affected by food shortages , such as the total number of food stamps in the world , and the total number of people affected by the total number of food in the world .